### TiendaBox - Pruebas del recurso Category
### Requiere: docker compose up -d  +  npm run dev
### En VS Code usar la extension "REST Client". Cada bloque se ejecuta con "Send Request".

@host = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Crear categoria -> 201 Created (copiar el "id" del body a @categoryId)
POST {{host}}/api/category
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Celulares",
  "description": "celuuuusss"
}

### Pegar aca el id devuelto por el POST anterior
@categoryId = 6a31a2872915ac8a7c6afde2

### 2. Crear categoria sin name -> 400 Bad Request
POST {{host}}/api/category
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 3. Crear categoria con name > 100 caracteres -> 400 Bad Request
POST {{host}}/api/category
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAX"
}

### 4. Listar todas las categorias -> 200 OK
GET {{host}}/api/categories

### 5. Obtener categoria por id -> 200 OK
GET {{host}}/api/category/{{categoryId}}

### 6. Obtener categoria inexistente -> 404 Not Found
GET {{host}}/api/category/000000000000000000000000

### 7. Actualizar categoria -> 200 OK
PUT {{host}}/api/category/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Notebooks y ultrabooks"
}

### 8. Actualizar con body vacio -> 400 Bad Request
PUT {{host}}/api/category/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 9. Actualizar categoria inexistente -> 404 Not Found
PUT {{host}}/api/category/000000000000000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Otra"
}

### 10. Eliminar categoria -> 204 No Content
DELETE {{host}}/api/category/{{categoryId}}

### 11. Eliminar de nuevo la misma categoria -> 404 Not Found
DELETE {{host}}/api/category/{{categoryId}}
